{"id":1735231,"retrievedAt":"2026-07-21T12:47:23.624Z","response":{"adult":false,"backdrop_path":null,"belongs_to_collection":null,"budget":0,"genres":[],"homepage":"","id":1735231,"imdb_id":null,"origin_country":["US"],"original_language":"en","original_title":"Maduku Telefon Bimbit","overview":"# Translation  The story of Salman and Mastura, a young middle-class married couple. Mastura loses patience with her husband Salman's behavior, who is constantly glued to his mobile phone as if she no longer exists. They frequently quarrel and have disagreements because of Salman's attitude. With no other options, Mastura seeks out Shafie, a marriage counselor. Looking at Mastura's dull appearance, Shafie suggests that she change her look. Mastura tries a modern appearance but it doesn't work either. Meanwhile, Mastura pretends to have a close relationship with Shafie and frequently uses her mobile phone. Salman begins to notice the changes in Mastura. He confronts her and Mastura threatens to divorce him and marry Shafie instead. Salman meets with Shafie and cries, begging Shafie not to take his wife. Only after that does he get an explanation that Shafie and Mastura were only pretending to be in love to make him realize that he is in love with his mobile phone.","popularity":0,"poster_path":"/ivS9NgkSZCqRYAEjNyT1MIxiDui.jpg","production_companies":[],"production_countries":[],"release_date":"2016-01-01","revenue":0,"runtime":0,"softcore":false,"spoken_languages":[],"status":"Released","tagline":"","title":"Maduku Telefon Bimbit","video":false,"vote_average":0,"vote_count":0,"alternative_titles":{"titles":[]},"credits":{"cast":[{"adult":false,"gender":2,"id":1518890,"known_for_department":"Acting","name":"Keith Foo","original_name":"Keith Foo","popularity":0.314,"profile_path":"/31Ds4O7QaVYWx9ndbofVf3x9JIR.jpg","cast_id":2,"character":"","credit_id":"6a5ef5c12eedf96084bb50f9","order":0},{"adult":false,"gender":1,"id":1155294,"known_for_department":"Acting","name":"Siti Sal